/* File:    resf.c
 * Purpose: Resource file processing
 * Author:  Ian Johnson
 * History: 22-July-93: IDJ:   created
 *          22-Apr-94:  IDJ:   module's resources get loaded into a single list.
 *          18-Dec-94:  IDJ:   bug-fix AQU-00289 - check for module resources already loaded
 *
